#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn46.40"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.40:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.40:0.2"
msgid "4. Nīvaraṇavagga "
msgstr "4. Hindrances "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.40:0.3"
msgid "40. Nīvaraṇasutta "
msgstr "40. Hindrances "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn46.40:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, nīvaraṇā andhakaraṇā acakkhukaraṇā aññāṇakaraṇā paññānirodhikā vighātapakkhiyā anibbānasaṃvattanikā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these five hindrances are destroyers of sight, vision, and knowledge. They block wisdom, they’re on the side of anguish, and they don’t lead to extinguishment. "

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.3"
msgid "Kāmacchandanīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave, andhakaraṇaṃ acakkhukaraṇaṃ aññāṇakaraṇaṃ paññānirodhikaṃ vighātapakkhiyaṃ anibbānasaṃvattanikaṃ. "
msgstr "Sensual desire, ill will, dullness and drowsiness, restlessness and remorse, and doubt. "

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.4"
msgid "Byāpādanīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.5"
msgid "thinamiddhanīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.6"
msgid "uddhaccakukkuccanīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.7"
msgid "vicikicchānīvaraṇaṃ, bhikkhave, andhakaraṇaṃ acakkhukaraṇaṃ aññāṇakaraṇaṃ paññānirodhikaṃ vighātapakkhiyaṃ anibbānasaṃvattanikaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn46.40:1.8"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca nīvaraṇā andhakaraṇā acakkhukaraṇā aññāṇakaraṇā paññānirodhikā vighātapakkhiyā anibbānasaṃvattanikā. "
msgstr "These five hindrances are destroyers of sight, vision, and knowledge. They block wisdom, they’re on the side of anguish, and they don’t lead to extinguishment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.98, sc2
msgctxt "sn46.40:2.1"
msgid "Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā cakkhukaraṇā ñāṇakaraṇā paññābuddhiyā avighātapakkhiyā nibbānasaṃvattanikā. "
msgstr "These seven awakening factors are creators of sight, vision, and knowledge. They grow wisdom, they’re on the side of solace, and they lead to extinguishment. "

msgctxt "sn46.40:2.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.40:2.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo, bhikkhave, cakkhukaraṇo ñāṇakaraṇo paññābuddhiyo avighātapakkhiyo nibbānasaṃvattaniko … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo, bhikkhave, cakkhukaraṇo ñāṇakaraṇo paññābuddhiyo avighātapakkhiyo nibbānasaṃvattaniko. "
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.40:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā cakkhukaraṇā ñāṇakaraṇā paññābuddhiyā avighātapakkhiyā nibbānasaṃvattanikā”ti. "
msgstr "These seven awakening factors are creators of sight, vision, and knowledge. They grow wisdom, they’re on the side of solace, and they lead to extinguishment.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.40:2.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.40:2.6"
msgid "Nīvaraṇavaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn46.40:3.1"
msgid "Dve kusalā kilesā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.40:3.2"
msgid "Dve yoniso ca buddhi ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.40:3.3"
msgid "Āvaraṇā nīvaraṇā rukkhaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.40:3.4"
msgid "Nīvaraṇañca te dasāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
